The reciprocal value of the PVAF is the capital recovery factor (CRF), which transforms a single present value or payment into T constant yearly payments NB in arrears (to be obtained after each year t; t = 1, …, T):6.8CRF=1PVAF=r1+rT1+rT−1.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
